#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:2
#: b1aa473d74244bffb01936e57f75b8ac
msgid "GitHub Discussions"
msgstr "GitHub Discussions"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:4
#: 2698dc39a2944aa4b310b8126c3ecf4c
msgid ""
"Long-form, searchable conversation that future users will find via Google — "
"questions with reusable answers, design proposals before a PR, and write-ups"
" of work built with TensorMesh."
msgstr ""
"适合长篇、可搜索的交流，将来的用户能通过 Google 找到——例如答案可复用的问题、提交 PR 之前的设计提案，以及基于 TensorMesh "
"完成工作的总结文章。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:8
#: 92423c319c9d4d10b0b027ae6045a220
msgid ""
"Use Discussions when you want the conversation to stick around. For a fast "
"back-and-forth, hop into :doc:`discord` instead; for a confirmed bug or a "
"concrete feature request, open a :doc:`github_issues`."
msgstr ""
"当您希望交流内容能长期保留时，请使用 Discussions。若需要快速的来回交流，请改用 :doc:`discord`\\ "
"；对于已确认的缺陷或具体的功能请求，请提交 :doc:`github_issues`\\ 。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:15
#: bf3df78d0fd64901a610ac5a372e56ca
msgid "Go to Discussions"
msgstr "前往 Discussions"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:33
#: f8732b7a7de143f08729fbfd474101d8
msgid ""
"You'll need a GitHub account to post or comment. Reading is open to "
"everyone."
msgstr "发帖或评论需要 GitHub 账号。阅读则对所有人开放。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:38
#: dbb936bb00af4a209732d6d8321ca288
msgid "Category guide"
msgstr "类别指南"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:40
#: 260ad36642cf4481813a06354841a778
msgid ""
"There are five categories, each tuned for a different kind of post. Pick the"
" one that matches what you're writing; if you're unsure, **General** is "
"always safe — a maintainer will move it if needed."
msgstr ""
"共有五个类别，每个类别针对一种不同类型的帖子。请选择与您所写内容相符的类别；如果拿不准，\\ **General** "
"总是稳妥之选——必要时维护者会将其移动到合适的类别。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:48
#: 443b747dd3344f4484fda603e4938ddd
msgid "Category"
msgstr "类别"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:49
#: 3322932772ac47e2b7a26e96c464646f
msgid "Format"
msgstr "形式"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:50
#: 1e2c64aee30c49d3a42566bd16b97126
msgid "What goes here"
msgstr "适合发布的内容"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:51
#: 36155cdc62174fc6ac17ef89daeeadea
msgid "**Announcements**"
msgstr "**Announcements**"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:52
#: 7e145d202cee46e789fe061ab138635c
msgid "Announcement (read-only)"
msgstr "公告（只读）"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:53
#: 2f7699cdad2a4bc6815b9185f6570411
msgid ""
"Release notes, API deprecations, scheduled breaking changes, community "
"events. Maintainer-posted. **Subscribe to this category** if you depend on "
"the library in production or in a paper."
msgstr "发布说明、API 弃用、计划中的破坏性变更、社区活动。由维护者发布。如果您在生产环境或论文中依赖本库，请\\ **订阅此类别**\\ 。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:57
#: d3a80287768e42ce9f1b97a2c5ea0130
msgid "**Q&A**"
msgstr "**Q&A**"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:58
#: 97247e67673d470ba5567daaca8c905e
msgid "Q&A (with *Mark as answer*)"
msgstr "问答（带有 *Mark as answer* 功能）"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:59
#: 73784a10562c433e8856dbc16390d1ae
msgid ""
"Usage questions, install / environment problems, \"how do I do X with "
"TensorMesh\". The OP — or a maintainer — marks one reply as the accepted "
"answer, which makes the thread useful to the next person who hits the same "
"problem."
msgstr ""
"使用问题、安装/环境问题、\"我该如何用 TensorMesh 做 X\" "
"之类的问题。发帖人——或某位维护者——会将某条回复标记为采纳的答案，从而让该帖对下一个遇到同样问题的人有所帮助。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:63
#: ad712960ca284c65b6fc39027aab008f
msgid "**Ideas & RFCs**"
msgstr "**Ideas & RFCs**"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:64
#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:71
#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:77
#: 979b3082b9d8447984e24cac4b5c4922 d57d57402c404c75b09875ec50176e3c
#: d96357a7b6be4cc7bc172fd1d3a4d44e
msgid "Open discussion"
msgstr "开放讨论"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:65
#: bac1aaea75a74967a05c513b5e40019b
msgid ""
"Proposals for new features, API design, breaking changes — *before* you "
"write the PR. Floating an idea here first usually saves a round of \"we'd "
"actually want this shaped differently\" review later. Link the eventual "
"issue / PR in a follow-up comment."
msgstr ""
"关于新功能、API 设计、破坏性变更的提案——在您编写 PR *之前*\\ "
"。先在这里抛出想法，通常能省去后续一轮\"其实我们希望它换一种形式\"的评审。请在后续评论中关联最终的 issue / PR。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:70
#: c9f324811865497094807e4326766056
msgid "**Show & Tell**"
msgstr "**Show & Tell**"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:72
#: 38d615700ae041beb948d87b4726172b
msgid ""
"Papers that used TensorMesh, simulation animations, blog posts, teaching "
"materials, comparison plots against other FEM stacks. Self-promotion is "
"welcome here — that's the whole point of the category."
msgstr ""
"使用了 TensorMesh 的论文、仿真动画、博客文章、教学材料、与其他有限元工具栈的对比图表。在这里欢迎自我推广——这正是该类别的意义所在。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:76
#: e9f611c9623644958b089f81419ce153
msgid "**General**"
msgstr "**General**"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:78
#: e80481a61c54435a9d886f3d8a20fc69
msgid ""
"Anything FEM-, PyTorch-, or PDE-adjacent that doesn't fit above. Catch-all."
msgstr "任何与有限元方法、PyTorch 或偏微分方程相关，但不适合归入上述类别的内容。包罗万象的类别。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:83
#: 1e87e336b5224189971639d38999b4c4
msgid "Writing a good Q&A post"
msgstr "如何写好一篇问答帖"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:85
#: 765310da729246c5a1bb83edb3cd9398
msgid ""
"The same checklist from the Discord help-channel guide applies, and matters "
"even more here because future readers will arrive at your thread via search "
"— they only have what you wrote. See :ref:`asking-well` for the full list. "
"The short version:"
msgstr ""
"Discord "
"求助频道指南中的同一份清单在这里同样适用，而且在这里更为重要，因为将来的读者会通过搜索找到您的帖子——他们能依据的只有您所写的内容。完整清单见 "
":ref:`asking-well`\\ 。简要版本如下："

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:90
#: 0d24fad75e9a4f0e930c350b70dfd24a
msgid "**What you ran** — a minimal, copy-pasteable snippet."
msgstr "**您运行了什么**——一段最小的、可直接复制粘贴的代码片段。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:91
#: 32562c1d2ce148eea432bad3d3242105
msgid "**What you saw** — the full traceback, in a code block."
msgstr "**您看到了什么**——完整的回溯信息，放在代码块中。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:92
#: b1e5068fbd7d41d1a47947d87b2580b4
msgid "**What you expected** — shape, value, or behavior."
msgstr "**您期望什么**——形状、数值或行为。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:93
#: c9901d3d4ae1461c9584d51e5e57315f
msgid ""
"**Versions** — output of ``python -c \"import torch, torch_sla, tensormesh; "
"print(torch.__version__, torch_sla.__version__, tensormesh.__version__)\"``,"
" plus OS and CUDA version if relevant."
msgstr ""
"**版本信息**——``python -c \"import torch, torch_sla, tensormesh; "
"print(torch.__version__, torch_sla.__version__, tensormesh.__version__)\"`` "
"的输出，以及（如相关）操作系统和 CUDA 版本。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:97
#: eb93e5d10baa47e2b2f406d8e92789a6
msgid ""
"A useful habit: when the issue is resolved, **edit the OP** to add a one-"
"line \"Resolution:\" summary at the top, so future readers don't have to "
"scroll through the back-and-forth. Then mark the answering reply."
msgstr ""
"一个有用的习惯：当问题解决后，\\ **编辑原帖**\\ "
"，在开头添加一行\"Resolution:\"（解决方案）摘要，这样将来的读者就无需翻阅来回的讨论。然后再标记出给出答案的那条回复。"

