#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:130
#: 0e7edfd953e54dcb8661f49b6409638a
msgid ""
"When in doubt: post to Discussions, link from Discord. Chat that sounded "
"one-off often turns out to be useful to others later, and moving a Discord "
"exchange into a Discussion thread is a maintainer- friendly thing to do."
msgstr ""
"拿不准时：发到 Discussions，并从 Discord 附上链接。看似一次性的聊天往往后来对他人很有用，而把一次 Discord 交流整理成一个 "
"Discussion 帖子，是一件对维护者很友好的事。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:137
#: f078637a51f3418a94ab71a677a90a11
msgid "Labels"
msgstr "标签"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:139
#: aac4c7d1f389448ba3f72f2d07ac9129
msgid ""
"Maintainers may tag Q&A discussions with labels like ``installation``, "
"``cuda``, ``meshing``, ``assembly``, ``solver``, ``autograd``, or ``docs`` "
"to make search filtering possible. You don't need to label your own post — "
"pick the right category, and the labels follow."
msgstr ""
"维护者可能会为问答类讨论打上诸如 ``installation``\\ 、\\ ``cuda``\\ 、\\ ``meshing``\\ 、\\ "
"``assembly``\\ 、\\ ``solver``\\ 、\\ ``autograd`` 或 ``docs`` "
"之类的标签，以便进行搜索过滤。您无需为自己的帖子打标签——只要选对类别，标签自然会随之而来。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:146
#: 5cbb4e9aa4064931bdf789adacb95b0e
msgid "Etiquette"
msgstr "礼仪规范"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:148
#: 66664787f9a1451cb36df13921970550
msgid ""
"The same norms that apply on :ref:`Discord <etiquette>` apply here: be kind,"
" keep disagreements technical, no spam. A couple of Discussions-specific "
"courtesies on top:"
msgstr ""
"适用于 :ref:`Discord <etiquette>` "
"的同一套规范在这里同样适用：保持友善、让分歧停留在技术层面、禁止垃圾信息。此外还有几条专门针对 Discussions 的礼节："

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:152
#: ce7d3610f2b54ca08508c059191799bc
msgid ""
"**Search before posting.** Many questions have already been asked. GitHub's "
"in-page search across Discussions is decent; a quick "
"``site:github.com/camlab-ethz/TensorMesh/discussions <your terms>`` on "
"Google is even better."
msgstr ""
"**发帖前先搜索。** 许多问题已经有人问过。GitHub 在 Discussions 内的页面搜索还不错；在 Google 上快速搜索 "
"``site:github.com/camlab-ethz/TensorMesh/discussions <your terms>`` 则效果更佳。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:156
#: ae27f0b40535493197d2b493819937a3
msgid ""
"**One topic per thread.** If you find yourself describing two unrelated "
"problems in the same post, split it. Threaded replies on Q&A only work well "
"when the question is single-shot."
msgstr ""
"**每个帖子只讨论一个主题。** 如果您发现自己在同一篇帖子里描述了两个不相关的问题，请将其拆开。问答区的串联回复只有在问题是单一问题时才能良好运作。"

#: ../../source/community/github_discussions.rst:159
#: a101a36c4b824655ba36a5c260311208
msgid ""
"**Don't open a duplicate.** If your problem matches an existing thread, "
"comment there instead of opening a new one — even if the existing thread is "
"closed. A maintainer will reopen it or redirect."
msgstr ""
"**不要重复开帖。** "
"如果您的问题与某个已有帖子相符，请在那里评论，而不要新开一个帖子——即便那个已有帖子已经关闭。维护者会重新打开它或将您引导到合适的地方。"
